<Link id="l00029" /><CodeLine lineNumber="29"><Highlight kind="comment">/// A Graph object represents a Directed Graph and is used in XRay to compute</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00030" /><CodeLine lineNumber="30"><Highlight kind="comment">/// and store function call graphs and associated statistical information.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00031" /><CodeLine lineNumber="31"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00032" /><CodeLine lineNumber="32"><Highlight kind="comment">/// The graph takes in four template parameters, these are:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00033" /><CodeLine lineNumber="33"><Highlight kind="comment">///  - VertexAttribute, this is a structure which is stored for each vertex.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00034" /><CodeLine lineNumber="34"><Highlight kind="comment">///    Must be DefaultConstructible, CopyConstructible, CopyAssignable and</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00035" /><CodeLine lineNumber="35"><Highlight kind="comment">///    Destructible.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00036" /><CodeLine lineNumber="36"><Highlight kind="comment">///  - EdgeAttribute, this is a structure which is stored for each edge</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00037" /><CodeLine lineNumber="37"><Highlight kind="comment">///    Must be DefaultConstructible, CopyConstructible, CopyAssignable and</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00038" /><CodeLine lineNumber="38"><Highlight kind="comment">///    Destructible.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00039" /><CodeLine lineNumber="39"><Highlight kind="comment">///  - EdgeAttribute, this is a structure which is stored for each variable</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00040" /><CodeLine lineNumber="40"><Highlight kind="comment">///  - VI, this is a type over which DenseMapInfo is defined and is the type</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00041" /><CodeLine lineNumber="41"><Highlight kind="comment">///    used look up strings, available as VertexIdentifier.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00042" /><CodeLine lineNumber="42"><Highlight kind="comment">///  - If the built in DenseMapInfo is not defined, provide a specialization</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00043" /><CodeLine lineNumber="43"><Highlight kind="comment">///    class type here.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00044" /><CodeLine lineNumber="44"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Graph is CopyConstructible, CopyAssignable, MoveConstructible and</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00046" /><CodeLine lineNumber="46"><Highlight kind="comment">/// MoveAssignable but is not EqualityComparible or LessThanComparible.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00047" /><CodeLine lineNumber="47"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00048" /><CodeLine lineNumber="48"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Usage Example Graph with weighted edges and vertices:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00049" /><CodeLine lineNumber="49"><Highlight kind="comment">///   Graph&lt;int, int, int&gt; G;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00050" /><CodeLine lineNumber="50"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00051" /><CodeLine lineNumber="51"><Highlight kind="comment">///   G&#91;1&#93; = 0;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00052" /><CodeLine lineNumber="52"><Highlight kind="comment">///   G&#91;2&#93; = 2;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00053" /><CodeLine lineNumber="53"><Highlight kind="comment">///   G&#91;&#123;1,2&#125;&#93; = 1;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><Highlight kind="comment">///   G&#91;&#123;2,1&#125;&#93; = -1;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><Highlight kind="comment">///   for(const auto &amp;v : G.vertices())&#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><Highlight kind="comment">///     // Do something with the vertices in the graph;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><Highlight kind="comment">///   &#125;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00061" /><CodeLine lineNumber="61"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00064" /><CodeLine lineNumber="64"><Highlight kind="comment">///    char va&#91;&#93; = &quot;Vertex A&quot;;</Highlight></CodeLine>
